answers.answer: Hi,How are you? What other symptoms are present? It is good to hear that you do not have any history of diabetes. If your urine does not come out or if you have difficulty urinating, this could be due to infection, prostate issues or bladder problems. Diagnostic tests such as urine test may help determine the underlying cause. If it persists, it is best that you have this checked by your doctor for proper evaluation. Take care and do keep us posted.
